#: ../../talk/index.rst:3
msgid "Talk"
msgstr "Talk"

#: ../../talk/index.rst:5
msgid ""
"Nextcloud Talk offers audio/video and text chat integrated in Nextcloud. It "
"is available as a web interface, desktop client, and mobile apps for Android"
" and iOS."
msgstr ""
"Nextcloud Talk propose des fonctionnalités de discussion audio/vidéo et en "
"mode texte intégrées à Nextcloud. Ce service est disponible sous formes "
"d'interface web, de client de bureau et d'applications mobiles pour Android "
"et iOS."

#: ../../talk/index.rst:8
msgid ""
"You can find out more about Nextcloud Talk `on our website "
"<https://nextcloud.com/talk/>`_. Download the desktop and mobile clients "
"from `nextcloud.com/install <https://nextcloud.com/install/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Pour en savoir plus sur Nextcloud Talk, rendez-vous `sur notre site web "
"<https://nextcloud.com/talk/>`_. Téléchargez les apps clientes pour "
"ordinateur et mobile sur `nextcloud.com/install "
"<https://nextcloud.com/install/>`_."
